          <p class='first-para'>
            Can the Minister tell me what has changed since 1996 when her right hon. Friend the
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_113wh' title='Col. 113WH &mdash; HC Deb 20 March 2002 vol 382 c113WH' name='column_113wh' href='#column_113wh' rel='bookmark'>113WH</a>
